'''毛囊'''（'''Hair follicle'''）是用來生長毛髮的皮膚器官，也是哺乳動物唯一終生呈週期性循環的器官，分布在除了手掌、腳掌和嘴唇以外的全身體表皮膚上。

毛囊可以幫助表皮維持機體免受外界環境的損傷，在生理性的組織更新和外傷修復中發揮重要作用<ref>{{cite journal |author1=吳桂菊 |author2=侯強 |author3=顧軍 |author4=劉繼勇 |title=人毛囊隆突區上皮幹細胞、黑素幹細胞及自發螢光存在的研究 |journal=上海交通大學學報(醫學版) |date=2016 |volume=36 |issue=10 |pages=1436-1439}}</ref>。

目前已有[[研究|研究]]發現與[[立毛肌|立毛肌]]接觸[[面積|面積]]越大的毛囊保持得越持久，而與立毛肌接觸面積越小的毛囊則更容易受到雄激素的[[刺激|刺激]]而轉變為[[毫毛|毫毛]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Sato |first1=A |last2=Toyoshima |first2=KE |last3=Toki |first3=H |last4=Ishibashi |first4=N |last5=Asakawa |first5=K |last6=Iwadate |first6=A |last7=Kanayama |first7=T |last8=Tobe |first8=H |last9=Takeda |first9=A |last10=Tsuji |first10=T |title=Single follicular unit transplantation reconstructs arrector pili muscle and nerve connections and restores functional hair follicle piloerection. |journal=The Journal of dermatology |date=2012-08 |volume=39 |issue=8 |pages=682-7 |doi=10.1111/j.1346-8138.2012.01505.x |pmid=22380609 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22380609/ |accessdate=2020-03-18 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326144353/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22380609/ |archive-date=2020-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。 

==結構==
[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]毛囊的基本結構都是相同的。毛囊由連接組織鞘（Connective tissue sheath、CTS）、[[內根鞘|內根鞘]]（Inner root sheath、IRS）、[[外根鞘|外根鞘]] （Outer root sheath、ORS）、毛球（Hair bulb）和毛幹（Hair shaft）等構成<ref name=def/>。

毛球內包圍著一些密集的真皮纖維細胞，內陷深入部分稱為毛乳頭（Dermal papilla、DP），是一個發送和接收信號的誘導結構<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Harmon |first1=CS |last2=Nevins |first2=TD |title=Hair fibre production by human hair follicles in whole-organ culture. |journal=The British journal of dermatology |date=1994-04 |volume=130 |issue=4 |pages=415-23 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2133.1994.tb03372.x |pmid=8186105 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8186105/ |accessdate=2020-03-24 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324153541/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8186105/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，毛乳頭由位於成群分布在毛囊基底部的真皮毛乳頭細胞（Dermal papilla cell、DPC）組成，可以誘導毛囊再生<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Moore |first1=GP |last2=Du Cros |first2=DL |last3=Isaacs |first3=K |last4=Pisansarakit |first4=P |last5=Wynn |first5=PC |title=Hair growth induction: roles of growth factors. |journal=Annals of the New York Academy of Sciences |date=1991-12-26 |volume=642 |pages=308-25 |doi=10.1111/j.1749-6632.1991.tb24397.x |pmid=1809090 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/1809090/ |accessdate=2020-03-24 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324153534/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/1809090/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。內根鞘是包圍毛幹的剛硬結構，決定毛幹的形狀，由鞘小皮、[[赫氏層|赫氏層]]（Huxley's layer）和[[亨氏層|亨氏層]]（Henle's layer）組成。外根鞘在內根鞘之外，由厚厚的細胞組成，包裹著整個內根鞘和毛幹。毛囊的最外面是連接組織鞘，由幾層[[成纖維細胞|成纖維細胞]]組成，將毛囊與真皮層隔離開<ref>{{cite journal |author1=楊衛兵 |author2=郝飛 |title=毛乳頭細胞在毛囊形態學發生和生長調控中的作用 |journal=國外醫學皮膚性病學分冊 |date=2003 |volume=29 |issue=5 |pages=312-313}}</ref>。

毛囊實際上由兩大部分組成，即上皮（毛母質與外根鞘）和真皮（毛乳頭和結締組織鞘），其中包括20多種細胞，包括角質形成細胞、黑色素細胞、[[蘭格漢氏細胞|蘭格漢氏細胞]]（Langerhans cell）、{{le|默克麥克氏細胞|Merkel cell}}（Merkel cell）、真皮鞘細胞和毛乳頭細胞<ref name=def>{{cite journal |author1=馬馨 |author2=陳洋 |author3=姜懷志 |title=哺乳動物毛囊結構特徵及調控機制 |journal=中國草食動物科學 |date=2013 |issue=1 |pages=53-56}}</ref>。

絕大多數哺乳動物毛囊分為兩類，即初級毛囊（Primary hair follicle、PF）和次級毛囊（Secondary hair follicle、SF）<ref name=def/>。初級毛囊發生較早，毛球大，毛囊較長和較粗，具有兩個發達的皮脂腺（Sebaceous gland、SG），毛幹一般有髓質<ref name=def/>。次級毛囊發生較晚，毛球小，毛囊短而細，沒有或僅有一個不發達的[[皮脂腺|皮脂腺]]，毛幹沒有髓質<ref name=def/>。大多數[[成年|成年]]的哺乳動物毛囊都是成群分布的，而每個毛囊群基本上由一至五個初級毛囊，以及圍繞在初級毛囊周圍的若干個次級毛囊組成<ref name=def/>。

==毛囊週期==
一般而言，毛囊的生長週期會經歷生長期（Anagen phase）、退行期（Catagen phase）和休止期（Telogen phase）三個階段<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Schmidt-Ullrich |first1=R |last2=Paus |first2=R |title=Molecular principles of hair follicle induction and morphogenesis. |journal=BioEssays : news and reviews in molecular, cellular and developmental biology |date=2005-03 |volume=27 |issue=3 |pages=247-61 |doi=10.1002/bies.20184 |pmid=15714560 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15714560/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130810/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/15714560/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mou |first1=C |last2=Jackson |first2=B |last3=Schneider |first3=P |last4=Overbeek |first4=PA |last5=Headon |first5=DJ |title=Generation of the primary hair follicle pattern. |journal=Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America |date=2006-06-13 |volume=103 |issue=24 |pages=9075-80 |doi=10.1073/pnas.0600825103 |pmid=16769906 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16769906/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130813/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16769906/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。毛囊是依靠上皮細胞和真皮[[間充質|間充質]][[細胞|細胞]]的相互作用，完成週期性生長，以發育成完整的毛囊<ref name=Wu>{{cite journal |author1=胡帥帥 |author2=張珉 |author3=肖葉懿 |author4=陳陽 |author5=鮑國連 |author6=吳信生 |title=不同毛色獺兔皮膚中黑色素沈積及毛囊發育規律 |journal=西北農業學報 |date=2019 |volume=28 |issue=9 |pages=1387-1393}}</ref>。毛囊發育的週期性不僅受光照、[[溫度|溫度]]及[[紫外線|紫外線]]等[[物理|物理]]因素的調控，還受相關基因及通路的調控<ref name=Wu/>。隨著毛囊週期的變化，毛囊周圍的毛細微血管也會出現變化，因為在毛囊生長期時，毛細微血管比較發達，而毛囊進入退行期後會逐漸退化<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Paus |first1=R |last2=Cotsarelis |first2=G |title=The biology of hair follicles. |journal=The New England journal of medicine |date=1999-08-12 |volume=341 |issue=7 |pages=491-7 |doi=10.1056/NEJM199908123410706 |pmid=10441606 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10441606/ |accessdate=2020-03-21 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130817/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10441606/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Yano |first1=K |last2=Brown |first2=LF |last3=Detmar |first3=M |title=Control of hair growth and follicle size by VEGF-mediated angiogenesis. |journal=The Journal of clinical investigation |date=2001-02 |volume=107 |issue=4 |pages=409-17 |doi=10.1172/JCI11317 |pmid=11181640 |accessdate=2020-03-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Mecklenburg |first1=L |last2=Tobin |first2=DJ |last3=Müller-Röver |first3=S |last4=Handjiski |first4=B |last5=Wendt |first5=G |last6=Peters |first6=EM |last7=Pohl |first7=S |last8=Moll |first8=I |last9=Paus |first9=R |title=Active hair growth (anagen) is associated with angiogenesis. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=2000-05 |volume=114 |issue=5 |pages=909-16 |doi=10.1046/j.1523-1747.2000.00954.x |pmid=10771470 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10771470/ |accessdate=2020-03-21 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130812/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/10771470/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===生長期===
這是毛囊生長最活躍的階段<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Baker |first1=RE |last2=Murray |first2=PJ |title=Understanding hair follicle cycling: a systems approach. |journal=Current opinion in genetics & development |date=2012-12 |volume=22 |issue=6 |pages=607-12 |doi=10.1016/j.gde.2012.11.007 |pmid=23313098 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23313098/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130815/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23313098/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，亦是
[[黑色素|黑色素]]生成和大部分哺乳動物週期經歷最長的一個階段<ref name=Chang/>。毛囊凸出區域的[[幹細胞|幹細胞]]迅速增殖，毛囊根部的毛乳頭不斷增大，並且開始向[[皮膚|皮膚]]深處生長<ref name=Chang/>。由於毛母質細胞受到毛乳頭的調控，快速分化出新的毛幹和內根鞘<ref name=Chang/>。一般來說，[[人類|人類]][[頭皮|頭皮]]毛囊的生長期可以持續2至8[[年|年]]，而[[眉毛|眉毛]]及[[睫毛|睫毛]]等毛囊的生長期只能維持2至3個月<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bernard |first1=BA |title=[The biology of hair follicle]. |journal=Journal de la Societe de biologie |date=2005 |volume=199 |issue=4 |pages=343-8 |doi=10.1051/jbio:2005036 |pmid=16738529 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16738529/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130812/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16738529/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。然而其他動物的情況未必與人類的情況一樣，例如絨山羊生長期不及6個月<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Galbraith |first1=H |title=Fundamental hair follicle biology and fine fibre production in animals. |journal=Animal : an international journal of animal bioscience |date=2010-09 |volume=4 |issue=9 |pages=1490-509 |doi=10.1017/S175173111000025X |pmid=22444696 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22444696/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130810/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22444696/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。目前已知拔毛法可以誘導功能正常的毛囊快速轉化進入生長期<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Müller-Röver |first1=S |last2=Handjiski |first2=B |last3=van der Veen |first3=C |last4=Eichmüller |first4=S |last5=Foitzik |first5=K |last6=McKay |first6=IA |last7=Stenn |first7=KS |last8=Paus |first8=R |title=A comprehensive guide for the accurate classification of murine hair follicles in distinct hair cycle stages. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=2001-07 |volume=117 |issue=1 |pages=3-15 |doi=10.1046/j.0022-202x.2001.01377.x |pmid=11442744 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11442744/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322130811/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/11442744/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===退行期===
退行期是毛囊從生長期過渡到休止期的過程<ref name=Chang/>。退行期時的毛母質細胞數目會減少，減慢毛幹和內根鞘的分化速度，而毛球和外根鞘亦開始凋亡<ref name=Chang/>。毛乳頭細胞處於縮聚狀態，毛囊變小且開始從真皮乳頭脫落<ref name=Chang/>。

===休止期===
休止期時的毛囊活動基本處於休眠狀態<ref name=Chang>{{cite journal |author1=常永芳 |author2=包鵬甲 |author3=褚敏 |author4=吳曉雲 |author5=梁春年 |author6=閻萍 |title=LncRNA在哺乳動物毛囊發育調控中的研究進展 |journal=生物技術通報 |date=2019 |volume=35 |issue=8 |pages=205-212}}</ref>。有研究指出臨床上休止期脫髮的產生與毛囊休止期的過度延長有關<ref>{{cite journal |author1=章星琪 |title=休止期脫髮診療新進展 |journal=中華皮膚科雜誌 |date=2017 |volume=50 |issue=5 |pages=388-390 |doi=10.3760/cma.j.issn.0412-4030.2017.05.024}}</ref>。

==調控==
調控毛囊週期性發育的信號通路有許多，包括Wnt、TGF-β、Notch、SHH、MAPK、BMP、Jak-STAT和TNF等，並且有研究表明Wnt信號通路和Wnt信號分子對毛囊發育起著重要的作用。

===Wnt信號通路===
第一個被發現的調控毛囊發育的通路是Wnt/β-連環蛋白信號通路，也被認為是最重要的通路<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Yu |first1=Nanlan |last2=Song |first2=Zhiqiang |last3=Zhang |first3=Kezhou |last4=Yang |first4=Xichuan |title=MAD2B acts as a negative regulatory partner of TCF4 on proliferation in human dermal papilla cells |journal=Scientific Reports |date=2017-09-15 |volume=7 |issue=1 |doi=10.1038/s41598-017-10350-w |url=https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-017-10350-w#citeas |accessdate=2020-03-22 |archive-date=2020-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200415012527/https://www.nature.com/articles/s41598-017-10350-w#citeas |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目前已知在毛囊形態發生及初級毛囊的形成中，必須要有Wnt信號的傳導<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Tsai |first1=SY |last2=Sennett |first2=R |last3=Rezza |first3=A |last4=Clavel |first4=C |last5=Grisanti |first5=L |last6=Zemla |first6=R |last7=Najam |first7=S |last8=Rendl |first8=M |title=Wnt/β-catenin signaling in dermal condensates is required for hair follicle formation. |journal=Developmental biology |date=2014-01-15 |volume=385 |issue=2 |pages=179-88 |doi=10.1016/j.ydbio.2013.11.023 |pmid=24309208 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24309208/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326113726/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/24309208/ |archive-date=2020-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而發揮作用的主要是經典途徑Wnt/β-連環蛋白信號通路。該信號通路核心因素為β-連環蛋白，在毛囊中主要表達於外根鞘、内根鞘、基質和毛幹，但是在毛乳頭細胞、毛母質細胞和外根鞘細胞的表達量最高<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Lin |first1=CM |last2=Yuan |first2=YP |last3=Chen |first3=XC |last4=Li |first4=HH |last5=Cai |first5=BZ |last6=Liu |first6=Y |last7=Zhang |first7=H |last8=Li |first8=Y |last9=Huang |first9=K |title=Expression of Wnt/β-catenin signaling, stem-cell markers and proliferating cell markers in rat whisker hair follicles. |journal=Journal of molecular histology |date=2015-06 |volume=46 |issue=3 |pages=233-40 |doi=10.1007/s10735-015-9616-5 |pmid=25832347 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25832347/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326113721/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25832347/ |archive-date=2020-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

Wnt信號通路對毛囊發育的調控作用主要通過對毛囊幹細胞、轉錄因子、Wnt信號分子等的調節來實現。Wnt信號通路可以調節毛囊幹細胞，例如在毛髮再生期間，毛胚芽和隆突處毛囊幹細胞中，β-連環蛋白的穩定表達可以活化LEF/TCF復合物，從而激活[[C-Myc|C-Myc]]、[[周期蛋白D1|周期蛋白D1]]等下游靶基因的轉錄，進而促進毛囊幹細胞的活化、增殖和定向分化，但是毛囊幹細胞在β-連環蛋白的表達數量較少時會分化為表皮細胞<ref>{{cite journal |author1=吳素芳 |author2=馬濤 |author3=李健宇 |author4=李建平 |author5=張巧靈 |title=調控毛囊發育的Wnt信號通路研究進展 |journal=動物醫學進展 |date=2019 |volume=40 |issue=4 |pages=92-95}}</ref>。

Kim等發現Dickkopfs會[[分泌|分泌]]一些富含着[[半胱胺酸|半胱胺酸]]的[[蛋白質|蛋白質]]，以及[[低密度脂蛋白受體|低密度脂蛋白受體]]相關蛋白，兩者結合後會抑制Wnt信號傳導<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kim |first1=D |last2=Garza |first2=LA |title=The Negative Regulator CXXC5: Making WNT Look a Little Less Dishevelled. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=2017-11 |volume=137 |issue=11 |pages=2248-2250 |doi=10.1016/j.jid.2017.07.826 |pmid=28967390 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28967390/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326113722/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28967390/ |archive-date=2020-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

Qiu等發現[[佛波醇-12-十四烷醯-13-乙酸酯|佛波醇-12-十四烷醯-13-乙酸酯]]可以激活毛囊幹細胞，因為它活化Wnt/β-catenin信號傳導，令毛髮再生<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Qiu |first1=W |last2=Lei |first2=M |last3=Zhou |first3=L |last4=Bai |first4=X |last5=Lai |first5=X |last6=Yu |first6=Y |last7=Yang |first7=T |last8=Lian |first8=X |title=Hair follicle stem cell proliferation, Akt and Wnt signaling activation in TPA-induced hair regeneration. |journal=Histochemistry and cell biology |date=2017-06 |volume=147 |issue=6 |pages=749-758 |doi=10.1007/s00418-017-1540-1 |pmid=28185006 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28185006/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326113724/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28185006/ |archive-date=2020-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此外，Liu等發現齊墩果酸通過Wnt/β-連環蛋白途徑，[[刺激|刺激]]毛母質細胞進行增殖和細胞分化，促進人類頭髮的生長，有助解決脫髮問題<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Liu |first1=B |last2=Chen |first2=X |last3=Yi |first3=H |last4=Han |first4=L |last5=Ji |first5=B |last6=Chen |first6=H |last7=Deng |first7=W |last8=Wan |first8=M |title=β-Catenin is involved in oleanolic acid-dependent promotion of proliferation in human hair matrix cells in an in vitro organ culture model. |journal=Fitoterapia |date=2017-09 |volume=121 |pages=136-140 |doi=10.1016/j.fitote.2017.07.007 |pmid=28723343 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28723343/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326113728/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28723343/ |archive-date=2020-03-26 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==影響因素==
===維生素A及其活性衍生物===
在毛囊的生長、分化和維持方面，[[維生素A|維生素A]]及其活性衍生物發揮着重要作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bergfeld |first1=WF |title=Retinoids and hair growth. |journal=Journal of the American Academy of Dermatology |date=1998-08 |volume=39 |issue=2 Pt 3 |pages=S86-9 |doi=10.1016/s0190-9622(98)70452-9 |pmid=9703131 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9703131/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060634/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9703131/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Fisher |first1=GJ |last2=Voorhees |first2=JJ |title=Molecular mechanisms of retinoid actions in skin. |journal=FASEB journal : official publication of the Federation of American Societies for Experimental Biology |date=1996-07 |volume=10 |issue=9 |pages=1002-13 |doi=10.1096/fasebj.10.9.8801161 |pmid=8801161 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8801161/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060649/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8801161/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。多年來的[[研究|研究]]工作發現局部應用[[維A酸|維A酸]]可以調控毛囊發育週期<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Bazzano |first1=G |last2=Terezakis |first2=N |last3=Attia |first3=H |last4=Bazzano |first4=A |last5=Dover |first5=R |last6=Fenton |first6=D |last7=Mandir |first7=N |last8=Celleno |first8=L |last9=Tamburro |first9=M |last10=Jaconi |first10=S |title=Effect of retinoids on follicular cells. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=1993-07 |volume=101 |issue=1 Suppl |pages=138S-142S |doi=10.1111/1523-1747.ep12363264 |pmid=8392099 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8392099/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060632/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/8392099/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、維生素A可以激活小鼠的毛囊幹細胞<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Suo |first1=L |last2=Sundberg |first2=JP |last3=Everts |first3=HB |title=Dietary vitamin A regulates wingless-related MMTV integration site signaling to alter the hair cycle. |journal=Experimental biology and medicine (Maywood, N.J.) |date=2015-05 |volume=240 |issue=5 |pages=618-23 |doi=10.1177/1535370214557220 |pmid=25361771 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25361771/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060639/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25361771/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>、維生素A可以調節頭髮週期和免疫反應<ref name=Duncan>{{cite journal |last1=Duncan |first1=FJ |last2=Silva |first2=KA |last3=Johnson |first3=CJ |last4=King |first4=BL |last5=Szatkiewicz |first5=JP |last6=Kamdar |first6=SP |last7=Ong |first7=DE |last8=Napoli |first8=JL |last9=Wang |first9=J |last10=King LE |first10=Jr |last11=Whiting |first11=DA |last12=McElwee |first12=KJ |last13=Sundberg |first13=JP |last14=Everts |first14=HB |title=Endogenous retinoids in the pathogenesis of alopecia areata. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=2013-02 |volume=133 |issue=2 |pages=334-43 |doi=10.1038/jid.2012.344 |pmid=23014334 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23014334/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060636/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23014334/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>等現象，同時亦有研究發現缺乏維生素A會導致頭髮稀少<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Everts |first1=HB |last2=Berdanier |first2=CD |title=Nutrient-gene interactions in mitochondrial function: vitamin A needs are increased in BHE/Cdb rats. |journal=IUBMB life |date=2002-06 |volume=53 |issue=6 |pages=289-94 |doi=10.1080/15216540213464 |pmid=12625367 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12625367/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060655/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12625367/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>和毛囊過度角質化<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wolbach |first1=S. Burt |last2=Howe |first2=Percy R. |title=TISSUE CHANGES FOLLOWING DEPRIVATION OF FAT-SOLUBLE A VITAMIN |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-experimental-medicine_1925-12_42_6/page/753 |journal=The Journal of Experimental Medicine |date=1925-12-01 |volume=42 |issue=6 |pages=753–777 |doi=10.1084/jem.42.6.753 |accessdate=2020-03-22}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1=Baldwin |first1=TJ |last2=Rood |first2=KA |last3=Kelly |first3=EJ |last4=Hall |first4=JO |title=Dermatopathy in juvenile Angus cattle due to vitamin A deficiency. |journal=Journal of veterinary diagnostic investigation : official publication of the American Association of Veterinary Laboratory Diagnosticians, Inc |date=2012-07 |volume=24 |issue=4 |pages=763-6 |doi=10.1177/1040638712445767 |pmid=22585959 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22585959/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060633/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22585959/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，然而過量的維生素A會導致毛囊發育出現[[畸形|畸形]]<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hardy |first1=MH |title=Glandular metaplasia of hair follicles and other responses to vitamin A excess in cultures of rodent skin. |journal=Journal of embryology and experimental morphology |date=1968-04 |volume=19 |issue=2 |pages=157-80 |pmid=4872188 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/4872188/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060637/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/4872188/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，而過量的視黃酸則會導致脫髮<ref name=Okano>{{cite journal |last1=Okano |first1=J |last2=Levy |first2=C |last3=Lichti |first3=U |last4=Sun |first4=HW |last5=Yuspa |first5=SH |last6=Sakai |first6=Y |last7=Morasso |first7=MI |title=Cutaneous retinoic acid levels determine hair follicle development and downgrowth. |journal=The Journal of biological chemistry |date=2012-11-16 |volume=287 |issue=47 |pages=39304-15 |doi=10.1074/jbc.M112.397273 |pmid=23007396 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23007396/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322060638/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23007396/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

維生素A通過影響脂類[[代謝|代謝]]或[[皮脂腺|皮脂腺]]功能，調節毛囊的發育。目前已知視黃酸可以[[抑制|抑制]]BMP2誘導的[[脂肪細胞|脂肪細胞]]分化，從而抑制[[過氧化物酶體增殖物活化受體γ|過氧化物酶體增殖物活化受體γ]]（PPARγ）的表達<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hisada |first1=K |last2=Hata |first2=K |last3=Ichida |first3=F |last4=Matsubara |first4=T |last5=Orimo |first5=H |last6=Nakano |first6=T |last7=Yatani |first7=H |last8=Nishimura |first8=R |last9=Yoneda |first9=T |title=Retinoic acid regulates commitment of undifferentiated mesenchymal stem cells into osteoblasts and adipocytes. |journal=Journal of bone and mineral metabolism |date=2013-01 |volume=31 |issue=1 |pages=53-63 |doi=10.1007/s00774-012-0385-x |pmid=23014973 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23014973/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322065800/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23014973/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。PPARγ在皮脂腺的發生過程中起主要作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Wang |first1=X |last2=Wang |first2=X |last3=Liu |first3=J |last4=Cai |first4=T |last5=Guo |first5=L |last6=Wang |first6=S |last7=Wang |first7=J |last8=Cao |first8=Y |last9=Ge |first9=J |last10=Jiang |first10=Y |last11=Tredget |first11=EE |last12=Cao |first12=M |last13=Wu |first13=Y |title=Hair Follicle and Sebaceous Gland De Novo Regeneration With Cultured Epidermal Stem Cells and Skin-Derived Precursors. |journal=Stem cells translational medicine |date=2016-12 |volume=5 |issue=12 |pages=1695-1706 |doi=10.5966/sctm.2015-0397 |pmid=27458264 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27458264/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322065801/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27458264/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，在啟動皮脂腺油脂細胞的[[細胞分化|細胞分化]]過程中發揮獨特作用<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Rosenfield |first1=RL |last2=Kentsis |first2=A |last3=Deplewski |first3=D |last4=Ciletti |first4=N |title=Rat preputial sebocyte differentiation involves peroxisome proliferator-activated receptors. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=1999-02 |volume=112 |issue=2 |pages=226-32 |doi=10.1046/j.1523-1747.1999.00487.x |pmid=9989800 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9989800/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322065814/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9989800/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，故而缺失PPARγ導致脫髮和皮脂腺萎縮<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Karnik |first1=P |last2=Tekeste |first2=Z |last3=McCormick |first3=TS |last4=Gilliam |first4=AC |last5=Price |first5=VH |last6=Cooper |first6=KD |last7=Mirmirani |first7=P |title=Hair follicle stem cell-specific PPARgamma deletion causes scarring alopecia. |journal=The Journal of investigative dermatology |date=2009-05 |volume=129 |issue=5 |pages=1243-57 |doi=10.1038/jid.2008.369 |pmid=19052558 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19052558/ |accessdate=2020-03-22 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322065823/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19052558/ |archive-date=2020-03-22 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

此外，維生素A可以調節毛囊發育相關基因及[[酶|酶]]類的表達。例如Duncan等指出參與維生素A代謝的[[基因|基因]]在斑禿病變中明顯上調<ref name=Duncan/>。Okano等指出皮膚中缺乏視黃酸降解酶{{le|CYP26B1|CYP26B1}}的[[小鼠|小鼠]]會出現毛囊發育缺陷<ref name=Okano/>。

==疾病==
===毛囊角化症===
[[毛囊角化症|毛囊角化症]]（Keratosis pilaris）是一種常見於[[中國|中國]]和[[日本|日本]]等[[國家|國家]]的常染色體顯性遺傳病，發生的原因是由於角質形成細胞的異常[[細胞凋亡|凋亡]]<ref name=sun>{{cite journal |author1=孫廷廷 |author2=朱小華 |title=毛囊角化症的病因 |journal=吉林醫藥學院學報 |date=2019 |volume=40 |issue=1 |pages=45-47}}</ref>，而臨床表現則為皮脂溢出部位出現多發的且小的紅褐色[[丘疹|丘疹]]，伴隨着瘙癢和疼痛，其他的皮膚表現包括掌跖角化性凹點以及甲萎縮<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Chacon |first1=GR |last2=Wolfson |first2=DJ |last3=Palacio |first3=C |last4=Sinha |first4=AA |title=Darier's disease: a commonly misdiagnosed cutaneous disorder. |journal=Journal of drugs in dermatology : JDD |date=2008-04 |volume=7 |issue=4 |pages=387-90 |pmid=18459521 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18459521/ |accessdate=2020-03-24 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324105916/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18459521/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。毛囊角化症造成的皮損常常隨著[[年齡|年齡]]的增長而逐漸減輕，甚至消失<ref name=sun/>。目前發現日光的照射、[[焦油|焦油]]、局部[[免疫缺陷|免疫缺陷]]導致的[[細菌|細菌]][[感染|感染]]、衣物摩擦和缺乏維生素A
都可以引起角化病<ref name=sun/>。

===倒置性毛囊角化症===
倒置性毛囊角化症（Inverted follicular keratosis、IFK）是一種內生性生長的毛囊漏斗部的良性腫瘤<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kenney |first1=M |last2=Lester |first2=EB |last3=Cook |first3=DL |title=Inverted follicular keratoses of the buttocks. |journal=Journal of cutaneous pathology |date=2018-05 |volume=45 |issue=5 |pages=369-370 |doi=10.1111/cup.13107 |pmid=29418015 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29418015/ |accessdate=2020-03-24 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324105920/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29418015/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，多見於50歲以上的老年患者，通常單發皮損，而九成的皮損好發於頭頸部，也可能發生於軀幹、四肢及[[女陰|外陰]]。IFK的表現通常為孤立的丘疹和結節，[[膚色|膚色]]或會變為深色，臨床表現缺乏特異性<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Noiles |first1=K |last2=Vender |first2=R |title=Are all seborrheic keratoses benign? Review of the typical lesion and its variants. |journal=Journal of cutaneous medicine and surgery |date=NaN |volume=12 |issue=5 |pages=203-10 |doi=10.2310/7750.2008.07096 |pmid=18845088 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18845088/ |accessdate=2020-03-24 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324105909/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18845088/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。有文獻指出多發的IFK提示着{{le|多發性缺陷瘤症候群|Cowden syndrome}}（Cowden syndrome）<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Larumbe |first1=A |last2=Iglesias |first2=ME |last3=Illarramendi |first3=JJ |last4=Córdoba |first4=A |last5=Gállego |first5=M |title=[Acral keratoses and inverted follicular keratosis presenting Cowden disease]. |journal=Actas dermo-sifiliograficas |date=NaN |volume=98 |issue=6 |pages=425-9 |pmid=17663933 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17663933/ |accessdate=2020-03-24 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324105914/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17663933/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

===毛囊性汗孔角化症===
毛囊性汗孔角化症（Follicular porokeratosis、FPK）通常被認為是汗孔角化病（porokeratosis、PK）的一種累及毛囊的少見[[病理學|病理學]]亞型，然而認為這是一種新臨床亞型的觀點沒有可靠的依據<ref name=Zhao>{{cite journal |last1=Zhao |first1=M |last2=Sanusi |first2=T |last3=Zhao |first3=Y |last4=Huang |first4=C |last5=Chen |first5=S |title=Porokeratosis with follicular involvement: report of three cases and review of literatures. |journal=International journal of clinical and experimental pathology |date=2015 |volume=8 |issue=4 |pages=4248-52 |pmid=26097620 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26097620/ |accessdate=2020-03-23 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323035445/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26097620/ |archive-date=2020-03-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。FPK的發病誘因可能是[[遺傳|遺傳]]、免疫抑制、感染和服用[[藥物|藥物]]等，表現為除掌跖點狀PK的其他PK亞型，包括Mibelli PK、播散性淺表性PK、播散性淺表光線性PK、線性PK和局限性PK<ref name=Zhao/>。大部分的FPK患者，用肉眼即可以看到皮損內的過度毛囊周角化現象，以及發現皮損周圍有著普通PK患者所有的典型環狀雞眼樣板層（Cornoid lamella、CL）<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Trikha |first1=R |last2=Wile |first2=A |last3=King |first3=J |last4=Ward |first4=KH |last5=Brodell |first5=RT |title=Punctate follicular porokeratosis: clinical and pathologic features. |journal=The American Journal of dermatopathology |date=2015-11 |volume=37 |issue=11 |pages=e134-6 |doi=10.1097/DAD.0000000000000319 |pmid=26485244 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26485244/ |accessdate=2020-03-23 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200323035445/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/26485244/ |archive-date=2020-03-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。有學者指出FPK的臨床表現特徵之處為環狀白色角質圍繞着毛髮，表面附著少量的細碎鱗屑，以及皮損周邊可以見到不連續的白色角質<ref>{{Cite thesis|degree=碩士 |title=毛囊性汗孔角化病一例和文獻復習|author=吳瓊 |year=2019 |publisher= 鄭州大學}}</ref>，而FPK的病理檢查特徵則為毛囊漏斗內可以見到角化不全性CL<ref>{{cite journal |author1=吳瓊 |author2=張雪嬌 |author3=董慧婷 |title=毛囊性汗孔角化病一例 |journal=中華皮膚科雜誌 |date=2018 |volume=51 |issue=4 |pages=317-318}}</ref>。

===頭部膿腫性穿掘性化膿性毛囊炎===
頭部膿腫性穿掘性化膿性毛囊炎（Perifolliculitis capitis abscedens et suffodiens、PCAS），亦稱為頭部膿腫性穿掘性毛囊周圍炎、頭皮分割性蜂窩織炎等，是一種少見的頭部慢性化膿性[[皮膚病|皮膚病]]，病原菌主要是[[葡萄球菌|葡萄球菌]]，而誘因主要是不注意[[衛生|衛生]]和搔抓，以及機體的抵抗力較低<ref>{{cite journal |author1=山凱萍 |author2=黃詠梅 |author3=王萍 |title=慢性化膿性穿掘性毛囊周圍炎病灶內光動力治療的臨床觀察 |journal=世界最新醫學信息文摘 |date=2019 |issue=95 |pages=88、90}}</ref>。

===嗜酸性膿皰性毛囊炎===
嗜酸性膿皰性毛囊炎（Eosinophilic pustular folliculitis、EPF），亦稱為Ofuji病（Ofuji’s disease），是一種毛囊丘疹性膿皰疾病<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nomura |first1=T |last2=Katoh |first2=M |last3=Yamamoto |first3=Y |last4=Kabashima |first4=K |last5=Miyachi |first5=Y |title=Eosinophilic pustular folliculitis: the transition in sex differences and interracial characteristics between 1965 and 2013. |journal=The Journal of dermatology |date=2015-04 |volume=42 |issue=4 |pages=343-52 |doi=10.1111/1346-8138.12783 |pmid=25675987 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25675987/ |accessdate=2020-03-23 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324030529/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25675987/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，最先由[[日本|日本]]學者所報道。目前仍然不清楚EPF的發病機制及病因，但是有指這是一種由各種[[抗原|抗原]]刺激有關的非特異性免疫反應<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Nervi |first1=SJ |last2=Schwartz |first2=RA |last3=Dmochowski |first3=M |title=Eosinophilic pustular folliculitis: a 40 year retrospect. |journal=Journal of the American Academy of Dermatology |date=2006-08 |volume=55 |issue=2 |pages=285-9 |doi=10.1016/j.jaad.2006.02.034 |pmid=16844513 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16844513/ |accessdate=2020-03-23 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324030531/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/16844513/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，甚至有認為EPF可能與機體對溶血性鏈球菌抗原產生的免疫反應有關<ref>{{cite journal |author1=敖俊紅 |author2=郝震鋒 |author3=楊蓉婭 |title=嗜酸性膿皰性毛囊炎 |journal=中國皮膚性病學雜誌 |date=2006 |issue=8 |pages=505-507}}</ref>。EPF的臨床表現包括紅斑基礎上的毛囊性丘疹及無菌性膿皰，邊緣可以向四周逐漸擴散而中央逐漸消退，並且伴隨着不同程度的瘙癢<ref>{{cite journal |author1=汪寧 |author2=徐妍 |author3=邊東亮 |author4=楊潔 |title=嗜酸性膿皰性毛囊炎1 例 |journal=世界最新醫學信息文摘 |date=2019 |issue=86 |page=243、250}}</ref>。

===播散性復發性漏斗部毛囊炎===
播散性復發性漏斗部毛囊炎（Disseminated and recurrent infundibulofolliculitis、DRIF）首次在1968年由Hitch和Lurid報道，首名被報道的患者是一名27歲的非裔[[美國|美國]]患者<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Hitch |first1=JM |last2=Lund |first2=HZ |title=Disseminate and recurrent infundibulo-folliculitis: report of a case. |journal=Archives of dermatology |date=1968-04 |volume=97 |issue=4 |pages=432-5 |pmid=5643238 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/5643238/ |accessdate=2020-03-23 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324030526/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/5643238/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，此後白種和黃種DRIF患者也陸續被報道，而發病年齡大約為2至55[[歲|歲]]，多數為[[青年|青年]]，男女均有。雖然有兄弟二人同患此病的案例<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Kline |first1=A |last2=Relic |first2=J |title=Disseminate and recurrent infundibulofolliculitis in childhood: a rarely reported entity. |journal=Pediatric dermatology |date=NaN |volume=32 |issue=1 |pages=e5-7 |doi=10.1111/pde.12442 |pmid=25644045 |url=https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25644045/ |accessdate=2020-03-23 |author= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324030525/https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/25644045/ |archive-date=2020-03-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，但是未見報道有家族史者。DRIF的病程長和易反復，其表現為夏重冬輕，發病突然，並且很快累及[[軀幹|軀幹]]和[[四肢|四肢]]，尤以頸胸部最明顯，多數患者自覺[[癢|瘙癢]]，部分患者瘙癢不明顯<ref>{{cite journal |author1=戚世玲 |author2=薛汝增 |author3=吉蘇雲 |author4=潘惠清 |author5=林爾藝 |author6=谷梅 |author7=吳鐵強 |title=播散性復發性漏斗部毛囊炎一例 |journal=中華皮膚科雜誌 |date=2017 |volume=50 |issue=10 |page=759}}</ref>。

===全毛囊瘤===
全毛囊瘤（Panfolliculoma）是一種罕見的毛囊[[良性腫瘤|良性腫瘤]]，最早於1993年由阿克曼等人命名。全毛囊瘤的臨床表現為慢性生長的囊性結節或類似囊腫的透明狀圓頂結節<ref>{{cite journal |author1=陳艷 |author2=楊希川 |author3=蘭雪梅 |author4=游弋 |author5=閻衡 |author6=尹銳 |author7=宋志強 |author8=鐘白玉 |author9=郝飛 |title=全毛囊瘤一例 |journal=中華皮膚科雜誌 |date=2016 |volume=49 |issue=4 |pages=286-287}}</ref>。

